{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"shape-rendering","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/shape-rendering","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n<p>指定 SVG 元素<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/path\"><code>&lt;path&gt;</code></a>的渲染模式。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用参考","title":"使用参考","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>类型</th>\n      <th>外观属性</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>值</td>\n      <td><strong>auto</strong> | optimizeSpeed | crispEdges | geometricPrecision | inherit</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>可运动</td>\n      <td>Yes</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"auto\">auto</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>让浏览器自动权衡渲染速度、平滑度、精确度。默认是倾向于精确度而非平滑度和速度。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"optimizespeed\">optimizeSpeed</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>偏向渲染速度，浏览器会关闭反锯齿模式。（速度）</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"crispedges\">crispEdges</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>偏向更加清晰锐利的边缘的渲染。浏览器在渲染的时候会关闭反锯齿模式，且会让线条的位置和宽度和显示器边缘对齐。（锐度）</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"geometricprecision\">geometricPrecision</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>偏向渲染平滑的曲线。（平滑）</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">version</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">shape-rendering</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>optimizeSpeed<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 这个示例在 Firefox 下看区别更明显 --&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>shape-rendering: geometricPrecision:\n        <img src=\"http://download.g63.ru/svg/shape-rendering-geometricPrecision.svg\" alt=\"shape-rendering:geometricPrecision\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </th>\n      <th>shape-rendering: optimizeSpeed\n        <img src=\"http://download.g63.ru/svg/shape-rendering-optimizeSpeed.svg\" alt=\"shape-rendering:optimizeSpeed\" loading=\"lazy\">\n      </th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n</table>\n<p>同样，你也可以在 CSS 样式中使用 shape-rendering:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">version</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>shape-rendering:optimizeSpeed;<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"关联元素","title":"关联元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下面的元素可以使用这个属性</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element#shape\">Shape elements</a> »</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://svgwg.org/svg2-draft/painting.html#ShapeRendering","title":"Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) 1.1 (Second Edition)"}],"query":"svg.attributes.presentation.shape-rendering"}}],"toc":[{"text":"使用参考","id":"使用参考"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"关联元素","id":"关联元素"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"shape-rendering","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"shape-rendering","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/shape-rendering","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/shape-rendering/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"